 * Loaded by docs/admin/index.html AFTER the main inline <script> and after
 * crm.js. Add before </body>:  <script src="/admin/marketing.js"></script>
 *
 * The base page exposes window.$ / window.esc / window.api (index.html line 139)
 * and uses a STATIC tab handler over ["leads","crm","listings","copy"] plus a
 * #savebar that only the listings/copy tabs use. This script injects two more
 * tab buttons + two <section> panels and hooks the existing tab machinery so
 * clicking a core tab clears the marketing panels and vice-versa.
 *
 * Reuses the page CSS (.panel .btn .btn.solid .btn.ghost .btn.sm .btn.danger,
 * --ink/--paper/--tint/--slate/--tide/--tide2/--line).
